&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These settings are important for building a website using hugo. See &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/configuration/#all-configuration-settings"&gt;All Configuration Settings&lt;/a&gt; for more details.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="header-anchor-wrapper"&gt;Site title
