&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Site title. This value will become the content of &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;title&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; tag in html.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Theme Settings</title><link>https://kaiiiz.github.io/hugo-theme-monochrome/configuration/theme/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>kaiiiz</author><guid>https://kaiiiz.github.io/hugo-theme-monochrome/configuration/theme/</guid><description>
